{"tid":2072913,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【618購物節】淘寶：母嬰產品銷售急升 4月交易額重返疫情前","createTime":"2020-06-21T03:14:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T03:21:50.000Z","uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b0f772c718959dd0979ff643a1390a2fae355f61","tid":2072913,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:14:35.000Z","msg":"【618購物節】淘寶：母嬰產品銷售急升 4月交易額重返疫情前<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/E9E1D-NsNNuHdEtzXQD8z7jssUQ=/802x451/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4QICSZTEPSKUYADRSA5OLDXMHU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FE9E1D-NsNNuHdEtzXQD8z7jssUQ%3D%2F802x451%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4QICSZTEPSKUYADRSA5OLDXMHU.jpg&h=217e6d0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天貓淘寶海外事業部港澳負責人陳子堅表示，疫情回穩後消費者購物習慣與去年比較明顯改變。<br />\n<br />\n中國疫情回穩，各大電商都推大型活動促銷。阿里（9988）旗下天貓淘寶海外事業部港澳負責人陳子堅表示，自今個月起舉行天貓618理想生活狂歡季（天貓618），活動首日淘寶直播全日成交金額（GMV）錄得超過51億元（人民幣，下同）。<br />\n<br />\n陳子堅表示，以中國市場計，消費者購物習慣與去年比較明顯改變，當中養生、家中娛樂、清潔用品銷售明顯增加。他特別提到近日母嬰用品銷售急升，料年底中國會掀生育潮。以平台GMV計，4月開始已回復疫情前水平，5月至今進一步復蘇。<br />\n<br />\n他又提到6月16日活動衝刺首一小時，電子產品類有25個品牌GMV為去年的10倍以上；有28個服飾品牌GMV已達去年全日的交易額，不少品牌都傾向以「雙店模式」，即品牌店及Outlet（特賣場）銷售。<br />\n<br />\n近月中國興起直播銷售，陳子堅稱活動期間有13個直播間GMV達1億元，而去年僅有2間。除了KOL及明星外，普通商家參與度佔整體達70%，6月初至今，平台直播次數達140萬場。<br />\n<br />\n對於直播銷售總收入會否只集中在KOL及明星，陳子堅解釋淘寶天貓亦會為小商戶提供培訓及協助，看到不少商家傾向薄利多銷，相信部份銷售會由線下轉到網上。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港方面，活動期間設100萬件商品包郵費，平均到貨日為3天。貨品方面，烘焙類、即食麵銷售按年有逾倍增長，相信與疫情有關。</span>而今年亦增設互動虛擬實境（VR）家居平台，傢俱銷售增速明顯。他亦指直播銷售在港亦是可行方案，為未來趨勢，會以本地化為目標。他亦指，香港消費者面對退貨困難問題，會與海關研究如何解決。<br />\n<br />\n記者：梁延宇"},{"pid":"24bc701e84af87c72d911b8cdada3b8f22d0876b","tid":2072913,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:15:49.000Z","msg":"FB香港人用成個月人工去淘寶<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6hxTD7Q.png&amp;h=816b1ac2&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登仔系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2062670/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2062670/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"c9d48ffb3b2749484b72f3beeb5245dbac0dcc17","tid":2072913,"uid":39871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:16:35.000Z","msg":"我的國終於要取代上水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc52c5bd155c9b6f47da436734f9a19e23422dfc","tid":2072913,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:16:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOYjrYXE.png&amp;h=38cc2f66&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"28a1e10da5caf8061e525affdbf4e4054af57d9d","tid":2072913,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:16:48.000Z","msg":"同瑞幸咖啡一樣，水份好高"},{"pid":"10927bddd9c4badbcdaea7610b261713eb3a94fb","tid":2072913,"uid":50972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28a1e10da5caf8061e525affdbf4e4054af57d9d","tid":2072913,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:16:48.000Z","msg":"同瑞幸咖啡一樣，水份好高"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:19:02.000Z","msg":"要睇埋退貨率 之後d購物節講緊30%起"},{"pid":"f1424669e274e97943603fa088d59c273aeaed34","tid":2072913,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc52c5bd155c9b6f47da436734f9a19e23422dfc","tid":2072913,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:16:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOYjrYXE.png&amp;h=38cc2f66&amp;s=540\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:20:48.000Z","msg":"波台狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vot4cHN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVot4cHN.png&h=021b7f20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n分化狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WRbpW9H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWRbpW9H.png&h=1a5acd25&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"19cacbb2145edaa396a5607936b6cd17037ef19c","tid":2072913,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:21:44.000Z","msg":"請善用起底功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e90a5bcea6e99a0e3a56052e640f3d01d51f159","tid":2072913,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:21:50.000Z","msg":"香港人連 民主黨 都投得落<br />\n用 TaoBao又有乜問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：TaoBao用戶"}],"pinned":{"pid":"24bc701e84af87c72d911b8cdada3b8f22d0876b","tid":2072913,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:15:49.000Z","msg":"FB香港人用成個月人工去淘寶<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6hxTD7Q.png&amp;h=816b1ac2&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登仔系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2062670/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2062670/page/1</a>"}}